{
  "stem": "7458.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the women just spent all of their time trying to somehow make meals out of next to nothing and to keep clean, because with so many people in one house, it was very easy to spread diseases and epidemics and so on.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So all in all-- and of course, the young men, the minute you would hear the German-- a German truck drove into town, you'd start running to hide.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nights were long.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Rumors would fly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Hope was practically nonexistent.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And people just tried to make the best of the situation, but it was not a very pleasant way of spending a day, day by day.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And of course, at least once a week there were actual killings, and you had to bury the dead.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Quite often, you had to go at night and dig them out from graves where the Germans dropped them and bring them to the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was-- life was actually preoccupied with death.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We continued to observe, but all of it was turned upside down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You couldn't really go to synagogues.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They actually closed the synagogues.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so, yes, you could pray in private.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You could celebrate in private.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You couldn't, for instance, bake matzoh for the holidays or openly celebrate anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we observed as best we could.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The events of late January [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] changed terribly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] 1943 was a very cold winter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The temperature had dropped to way below zero, and we had lots of snow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] In the middle of the night, we heard trucks.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
